Hi <%= @visitor.first_name %>,
<br><br>
Here's a list of all the new hosts available for your visit to <%= @visit.city %>:

<% @host_data.each do |listing| %>
  <%= listing[:host].first_name %> signed up as a host <%= listing[:hosting].distance_from(@visit).round(1) %> mi. from <%= @visit.city || @visit.zipcode %>.
  <br><br>

  <% unless listing[:hosting].comment.empty? %>
    Message from <%= listing[:host].first_name %>:<br>
    <%= listing[:hosting].comment %><br>
  <% end %>

Do NOT reply to this email! In order to contact these hosts, <%= link_to "follow this link", visit_url(@visit) %><br><br>

We strongly recommend that potential hosts and visitors connect over social media before making any housing plans.<br><br>

If you have already found a host or want to stop receiving emails, update your search at: <%= link_to "Your Visit Page", edit_visit_url(@visit) %>
<% end %>
